      <title>交易员保罗·帕克加入健康风险投资公司 Flagship Pioneering</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/dealmaker-paul-parker-joins-health-vc-firm-flagship-pioneering</link>
